==English==
===Etymology===
From French ''[[solidifier]]''

===Verb===
'''to solidify'''
#''(transitive)'' to make [[solid]]; convert into a solid body.
#''(transitive)'' to [[concentrate]]; [[consolidate]].
#''(intransitive)'' to become solid; to [[freeze]]

